    "updated": "Added: Micrococcus, Erysipelothrix, Gardnerella, Arcanobacterium, Pasteurella; Detailed Enterobacterales TSI decision trees; Full Vibrio NaCl patterns; Shewanella, Elizabethkingia details; Klebsiella/Serratia/Enterobacter species tables"
